dataset.title: Municipality

dataset.description:
This item is a zip file that contains the contents listed below.  This allow users with ArcGIS for Desktop the ability to download current Linn County imagery through the selection of tiles.

For detailed instructions, please read the steps outlined in the ReadMe.pdf document.

Items included:
  1. ImageryDownload.mpk -- This is a map package that when unpackaged, contains a map document (.mxd) with 2 web service layers.  One is a reference layer used to orientate the user.  The second is a current image service layer by which the user can download selected tiles to their local machine or shared network drive.
  2. _ReadMe_.pdf -- This is a PDF document that outlines the steps necessary for a user to download imagery (raster) tiles to their local machine or shared network drive.  Please consult this documentation for a step-by-step workflow.

Additional Resources
Esri documentation for downloading rasters using an image service.
